ar streams, event analysis.<\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/channel\/UCOdQ0NsfHy5dGobCeVakikQ\">Poisson<\/a> &#8211; Russian-language videos, Altar showcases, battle showcases.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baba Yaga Alliance War &#8211; Event Details:<\/strong><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh6.googleusercontent.com\/-bklfbxVo-Wfldfcqxejewt_BfsO80vURTFC1NDXMTEr7rcIn55iRtGV2xwrJ03OVMCa2m-zht8UMPV4ga450rdQp-G3zSLgb3iwkdw06Od71Xw9zMhjeYBHUJPKKbxsbcqoLpq5\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Baba Yaga &#8211; the totemic, supernatural ancestress &#8211; appears from the depths of the forest!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Congratulations to the winner of the Design-a-Titan contest, <strong>TALON WARLOK<\/strong>, for their incredible Baba Yaga design.<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Baba Yaga arrives with long-forgotten arcane magicks, utilising the collective power of the undead to reach unimaginable strength. Her skills are:<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>INVOKE: Dark Command<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>180% Titan Damage<\/li><li>+300% Raise Dead Skeleton Damage<\/li><li>On each Raise Dead cast, increase Horde Damage 25%<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baba Yaga\u2019s Hatred X<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>88% Titan Armor Piercing<\/li><li>+176% Horde Armor<\/li><li>+1 Raise Dead Spell<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baba Yaga\u2019s Magic X<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>117% Titan Health<\/li><li>+234% Horde Health<\/li><li>+1 Raise Dead Spell<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Baba Yaga\u2019s Resilience X<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>72% Horde Critical<\/li><li>72% Raise Dead Critical<\/li><li>+2 Raise Dead Spells<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>INVOKE: Bone Shards<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>30% Titan Melee Resist<\/li><li>30% Horde Melee Resist<\/li><li>On each Raise Dead cast, increase Horde Armor Piercing 25%<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>She brings with her two new Relics:<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"w