 imbalance, with many resorting to prayer and sacrifice in the hope that new Gods will answer their cries for help. Out in the furthest reaches of the universe, these cries have been heard&#8230; <\/em><em><br><\/em><em>Long forgotten deities stir\u2026 <\/em><em><br><\/em><em>War is coming!<\/em><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The New Gods are almost here. Get ready for the dynamic power of <strong>INVOKE<\/strong> skills, granting <strong>wide-ranging abilities<\/strong> that <strong>change battles<\/strong> like never before.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Divine Shrine Update:<\/strong><br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We are working hard to make improvements to the Divine Shrine. New content will soon be added, alongside some changes to the Altars themselves.&nbsp; Make sure to check our Facebook page for any updates, with more information on the content, changes and release date in next week\u2019s blog post.<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>Dom and Haig will return to the Dawn of Titans Livestream soon, but in the meantime, do visit, like, subscribe and follow our various social channels to get the latest information and updates on the game:<br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/dawnoftitansofficial\/\">Facebook<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/DawnOfTitans\">Twitter<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/dawnoftitans\/\">Instagram<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/dawnoftitans\">YouTube<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>And as always, we\u2019ll <em>see you on the battlefield!<\/em><br><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Titans! Due to scheduling situations, the Dawn of Titans team will not be able to bring you our scheduled Livestream over the next few weeks.&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories"